     - Olivier Delhomme <olivier.delhomme@free.fr>
        * Tests done with GFileMonitor and inotify. They suffers from
          limits : 1024 directories/files is the limit for GFileMonitor
          and 8192 is the limit for inotify (on my system). It seems that
          the only way to do this is to get the notifications directly
          from the kernel : redirfs or pluginfs ?

